Assignment Cold/Hot Publisher

* Create a Flux to check revenue for specific categories purchase

* Assumptions

    - product should have name , quantity , price, category
    - the flux should drop the item that have not one of the allowed categories
    - if the item has one of the allowed category should calculate the revenue and update the quantity
    - you can consider allowed categories 'Kids' and 'Automotive'.

* Expectations

    - should be possible to check every period of time the revenue and stock of allowed categories
